        {
          "source": "S5",
          "quote": "It involves extracting topics at the sentence level from individual documents, then aggregating and condensing these topics into a predefined quantity"
        }
      ],
      "reason": "The article reports a domain application (topic modeling) of an LLM without describing the prompt method in actionable detail."
